 Apocalypse screamed out. "Fall back!" The four horsmen pulled out and flew 
jet spped at full power." 
 Proto1000 wasnt going to stand by and die for these strangers. He pulled his 
hand out. No doubt ripping apart aracnia's spark. (She should be dead cuz 
getting 20 spikes pulled out of your chest should destroy her spark. Also 
remember hell beast is doomed. He has about 30 sec now to live. He should be 
unconsious. Remember the virus is ever changeing and no cure will ever be 
made in time to save him.)
 Apocalypse hated this. Death didnt wait to see the damage of his reaper. He  
powered his jet pack and flew off. 
 The 12ft red dragon went to beast mode and flew off. (you can shoot at the  
as they leave though I dont your troops will have the health to do so.)
 The bots locked onto drillbit's signal and flew towards it.
